Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:05.15,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes and dreams are the \Npower that moves humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:07.36,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,and keep the Earth turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:10.36,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow doesn't come because \Nthe sun rises in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.74,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,The sun rises in the morning \Nbecause people keep their
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.57,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,hopes close to their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.28,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i0} keep the Earth turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.92,Default,Gan,0000,0000,0000,,We are the passionate heroes, \Nthe Gambaraijers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.17,Default,UPS,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:43.63,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.50,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:51.89,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.20,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,So bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,How did Mom write songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.85,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.75,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.49,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The normal way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:24.30,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She'd sing, and then sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the melody already in her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.56,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Or did it come as she went along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.40,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, a cat could \Nput a song together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.13,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,if all the parts were already \Nfloating around in its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.74,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But is that really all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,There must be more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.76,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm only an expert at listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.82,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think you \Nneed to force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.70,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.51,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.79,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should talk to Shiho-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.92,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,They went to school together, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.47,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:10.93,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 9 \NTurning White and Turning Red
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,There are other jobs out \Nthere that involve horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.77,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:19.92,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.24,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no weight limit for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.93,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You're so insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.35,Default,tan,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:26.32,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,My weight's not an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:30.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't picture \Nmyself being happy with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.37,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,other people riding \Nthe horses I raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.47,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,That's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I have an announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,For the upcoming White Festival, \Nour very own choir club...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.89,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes badminton club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.12,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Musical Drama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.14,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,...will perform a musical drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.87,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,A musical drama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, singing is our top priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:04.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to include a solid story, dancing, \Ngreat costumes, and a real stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.33,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Who'll do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.32,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,And how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the scriptwriter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And Wakana's already \Nwriting a song, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We can use that \Nas our featured piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're writing a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.16,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't written anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.27,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.60,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, you'll handle choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:23.61,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Choreography?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. You've got the best moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka and Wien can take care \Nof the stage and props,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll all pitch \Nin to make costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.10,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You sound pretty serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.11,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.44,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Almost too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:38.31,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This'll cost a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.51,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely. At least 10,000-20,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.86,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Does the White Festival \Neven give budgets that high?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,So then, you have \Nother sources lined up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're here to brainstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.86,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.95,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Work these things out in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.49,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:57.08,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not going to do any "my love,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.62,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,my heart, I'll die without you" stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.09,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You asking for a kissing scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.77,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.50,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wien, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.70,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.55,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.05,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been listening \Nand taking notes, like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.35,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't need notes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.01,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sawa, how busy \Nis Shiho-san these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.38,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,My mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.61,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,No busier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please take a look at the \Ndocuments in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.99,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Western Shopping District Event Planning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.99,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\a6}Let's make this summer a hot one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A comparison of the district's revenue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.74,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,between this summer and last
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,indicates we're having \Na rather rough year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we're in quite a tight spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but that's just \Na sign of the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.32,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,And we're not getting any younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sakazaki-san's in the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He went for a full check-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.50,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he does eat an awful lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.21,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please refrain \Nfrom personal conversations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.02,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.22,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need an explanation, \Nwe can just read it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.81,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I should give you a \Nrundown, before we started strategizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If we all put in a little elbow \Ngrease, it'll all work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.02,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats honest effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:07.39,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you heard \Nabout Eikodo's girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.75,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Word is, she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.82,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,How about local superheroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.41,Default,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Local superheroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.25,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:18.50,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,You mean mascots?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.19,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We need more than \Njust people in costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.32,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We need superheroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:26.34,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Like the ones in groups of red, \Nwhite, yellow, and green.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.92,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please clarify \Nwhat you're suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.55,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,They could do "So-and-So Superhero! \NSo-and-So Ranger!" moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:35.18,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,and hand out store flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:37.14,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,Like a sandwich board campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:40.28,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty good idea, Shiho-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.73,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I've already got an \Nidea for the costumes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.23,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so all that's left is to \Nchoose our heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.15,Default,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I exhausted these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shake these headaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.57,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I need at least three volunteers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.57,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}My back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.10,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,though I'd prefer five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.49,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd like to give \Nour shopping district a—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.14,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.15,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:08.19,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.32,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.22,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana has some questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.81,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.33,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys heading home \Nfrom your club meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.00,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have five people there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.35,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.56,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect! Bring them all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.55,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you all \Nto some delicious cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.21,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure they come. I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:32.42,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get some delicious \Ncake over here, on the double.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.95,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're not gonna turn down cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.33,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.33,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Then Tanaka can come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You think Shiho-san can help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wein could take the train with Konatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:49.29,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to figure out what my mom thought \Nabout when she wrote songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.88,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Like if she ever felt scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:54.55,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Scared? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.79,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Like, if she ever doubted herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.79,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,or worried if the finished \Nproduct was any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:04.52,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I just... I need to \Nknow more about my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.44,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,if I'm going to write a song with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:07.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That's deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.79,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.28,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, everyone! Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.18,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.90,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.99,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.58,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you like \Nto make some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.58,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We sure would!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.25,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I was taught never to get roped in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.55,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,by slick talk or fast roller coasters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.68,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.09,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you like to be superheroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.68,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.89,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Want the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:49.63,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.56,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Suits and masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:56.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.02,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.58,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Superhero outfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.56,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Red, pink, yellow, white...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.79,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.92,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,They look perfectly usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.04,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's green, too. Just like the Gambaraijers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.09,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, what is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:14.10,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,These were used for a lunch box contest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Aren't these a bit small?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They're soft, so you can stretch them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.88,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,in the shopping \Ndistrict a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, hey. There're boots, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.66,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You wore those?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They're pretty old, but the sizes should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,For a lunch box contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:22.59,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we overstuffed it and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wow, they really do stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't believe these were hidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.79,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Our ambitions didn't fit in the box!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop talking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.66,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The association's hoping \Nyou'll wear them this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.94,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,How does 30,000 yen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.99,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,For all five of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.48,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,When would we start? \NHow many hours would we work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:39.86,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If we could use all five \Nof you, it'd be ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.80,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like you to do ten-minute shifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.65,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,five times each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:46.54,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,30,000 yen for a weekend's \Nwork is fair, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.83,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We'd also need time to rehearse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.01,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.13,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for sure, daughter of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana wants to ask \Nyou about her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.79,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Then if you scratch my back, I'll scratch yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.36,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.26,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.61,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only ones I can \Nask to be superheroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.01,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,This is a worthy mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.99,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,It's worthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:17.47,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,because it inspires hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.34,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes and dreams are the \Npower that moves humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.32,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,and keep the Earth turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wien?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.03,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow doesn't come because \Nthe sun rises in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.50,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,The sun rises in the morning \Nbecause people keep their
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.29,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,hopes close to their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.01,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We{\i10} keep the Earth turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.16,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.31,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,How could I allow myself to lose hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.71,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please repeat our job description?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:47.03,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... We'd like you to work over \Nthe weekend, for ten minutes at a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wien sure is passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.71,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Was he always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.39,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That was Gamba Red's speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.72,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,"The passionate heroes, the Gambaraijers."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.43,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We saw them in his room, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.03,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,So this flipped his superhero switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.54,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,So, you guys are in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:03.91,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We can rehearse tomorrow at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.04,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Not wasting any time, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.30,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.76,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know how \NMahiru wrote her songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.48,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was only ever a singer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.50,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,She was easy to talk to, \Nbut I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.88,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,that subject ever came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.34,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.49,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw her worry \Nmuch about that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.44,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure she was the \Ntype to let inspiration strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.23,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.94,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had talked to her \Nmore about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.74,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want to know \Nmore about composition,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.56,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,you should talk to the vice principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.05,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The song on that cassette tape
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:57.78,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,was co-written by her and your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:02.73,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiru told us she wanted \Nus to write our own song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.33,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,At first, we all thought she was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:08.30,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,But Takakura has \Nalways been quite serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.51,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,so she got swept up \Nin the whole affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.01,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We were surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:16.02,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,when they actually \Nfinished a real song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.26,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sweet song, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.50,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.04,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Takakura could be hard \Nto approach at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.17,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but I think she was someone \Nwe could look up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.79,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.38,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for telling me all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.71,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.25,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.57,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,What is a song, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.63,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:23.34,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with a concept \Nfor the superheroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.17,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:27.89,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Western Shopping District Heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:29.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,WestStoprangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.56,Default,waka,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a "sh."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.73,Default,sawa,0000,0000,0000,,ShopRangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.84,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Since we represent the \NWestern Shopping District,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:35.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.48,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So, no twist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The WestShopRangers are here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:43.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the peace of the galaxy \Nand of our valued customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,These heroes of justice will \Nensure you enjoy your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:51.00,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Meat Red? Fruit Pink? Whitebait White?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.90,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Actually, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.51,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really wearing these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.79,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing which color?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.58,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I like red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.04,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, red is for the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.42,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Favorite colors don't come into play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.27,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.29,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if you think \Nyou're ready to be Red,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.84,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I will do the right thing and step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.01,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.77,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask if you truly \Nare ready to be Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Red's qualifications are a sense of justice—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, no, no, I've got no \Nqualifications at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with Pink, Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You can be Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:27.32,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then Miyamoto's Curry Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.43,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,There's no curry place \Nin the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:36.63,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of asking you to \Nmake us a theme song, Wakana,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,but since you're busy writing \Nour song for the White Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.59,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,we can just use the \NGambaraijers theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The most important thing \Nis their trademark phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.88,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Full Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.46,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.50,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Meat Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.76,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, you're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.74,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.45,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Straight from the source!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:00.04,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bursting with flavor! Whitebait White!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.76,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,You need to sound cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.73,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are never gonna buy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:05.40,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.35,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Vitamins, minerals, and nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.35,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Veggie Green supports good health!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.00,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Put more feeling into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.96,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,And do a pose with each word!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:15.99,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wakana, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:20.91,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You first, Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:26.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Curry Yellow loves curry! Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.29,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Try what, some roux?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.67,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.51,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Be serious, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.14,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,This might just be a small \Nshow in a small town,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:39.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,but being superheroes for little kids
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.98,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,is an important mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:43.81,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.77,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's just to draw crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.40,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:50.19,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Air mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.79,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:03.76,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'd mailed them to a friend in \NWien, but they were sent back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:04.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.70,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.01,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,It says there's \Nno person named "Jan"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.51,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,living there anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.01,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,so I should stop sending letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried calling their \Nphone or texting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.44,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Jan's just a kid. He'll \Nturn seven this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.25,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We'd watch the Gambaraijers video \Nmy grandpa sent, on repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.65,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Gamba Red was our hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.05,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,But then I had to move back to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.00,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.43,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.26,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.01,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gamba Red will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.40,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.98,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you write to me,\Nonce you're back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.90,Default,Jan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to know more about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.02,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You bet I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:19.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Did you write about cultivating \Nexcellence and saying "to arms"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,And the white rhino \Nin the school's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.40,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.57,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad it all came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:31.92,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Wien...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:32.75,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.48,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling I'll \Nsee Jan again, someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.31,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, all I can do is trust Jan is doing his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.72,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,As a West Shopping District Hero. As Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:44.85,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.47,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought of a new pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.14,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Straight from the source!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.36,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bursting with flavor, Whitebait White!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.09,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,That's way better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:54.58,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.54,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You see the whitebait, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.34,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,If you move like this, \Nit'll look even more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.24,Default,tai,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.01,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this doesn't come with a skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It'll show everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.74,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess these characters \Nwere supposed to be boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.21,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.61,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! You have a great figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.02,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't actually see \Nunderwear through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.88,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't need skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:18.89,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,This smells like the main hall at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Like the temple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.90,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guys hurry up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.12,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.46,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Open that door and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.67,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, it ripped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.28,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,It did? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.37,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.03,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.00,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.16,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.83,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.70,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.35,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I was against it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.40,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,But even as principal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.72,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also an employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:56.23,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,If my superiors—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.23,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:00.59,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too sudden. \NIt's irresponsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.09,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Can you honestly accept this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.98,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:08.89,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,all the feelings and \Nhard work from the days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.73,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,when you were the choir club's advisor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:15.90,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.50,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Shirohamazaka High School Rule 18:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.83,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Except in special circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.17,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,students are prohibited from \Nhaving after-school jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:40.21,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this qualify \Nas a special circumstance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're raising money \Nfor the White Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.77,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.87,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,The vice principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.41,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:47.41,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ain't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.18,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Well, worrying won't solve the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.94,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Vice Principal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.39,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,we've come to ask permission \Nto have an after-school job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to perform at the White Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.12,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,the choir club needs to raise funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:11.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It would be different if we were given
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.30,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,an ample budget, like the main choir,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,but our club is poorer \Nthan a church mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.54,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Jobs are allowed if there is \Na special circumstance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.83,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly that kind \Nof special circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:23.97,Default,vice,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:29.60,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Um, we'd like your stamp of approval...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.97,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:20.08,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:21.14,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.55,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the vice principal \Nwas acting kind of weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:26.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:26.04,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.04,0:23:27.32,Default,dai,0000,0000,0000,,It was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.26,Default,wien,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Konatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:32.22,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You came in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.34,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Beta Carotene Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.39,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Curry Punch!
