Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:38.23,Default,sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Mango Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.14,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Your tempo and timing are horrible!
